        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This cypress onusa rod is decorated with a number of paper streamers that rustle when shaken to direct purification magic. Wands of purification contain either *cleanse affliction*, *clear mind*, or *sound body*, decided when the wand is created.",
        "level": 6,
        "traits": [
